<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>• رواه أبو داود <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c2">(٢٨٤٣)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وزاد فيه رزين:</span> <span class="c1">"ونسميه"</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
